When he tells me he has something to tell me,
I am still swayed like this.

271
00:26:09,300 --> 00:26:14,000
♫ Just wait for me on the morning when there's no news ♫

272
00:26:14,000 --> 00:26:20,300
♫ Don't tell me.  Please just stay with me. ♫
Let's meet briefly. I have something to tell you.

273
00:26:20,300 --> 00:26:24,840
When he tells me he wants to see me, I am still very swayed.

274
00:26:24,840 --> 00:26:28,910
I really am a fool.

275
00:26:28,910 --> 00:26:32,860
♫ My memories that I loved changed. ♫

276
00:26:32,860 --> 00:26:36,520
